description.en: This project, created to protect the environment, promotes the elimination of transactions in physical currency in favor of the circulation of virtual currency. in this way it will be possible to reduce the consumption of papers, inks and chemicals and to counter the spread, through the exchange of coins and banknotes, of viruses, bacteria and dangerous contaminants for humans.
